evaluated.description: iQPARK is an interactive entertaining and educational science centre situated in Liberec, Czech Republic intended mainly for younger children from 2 to 10 and their parents. It is the first venue of its kind in the Czech Republic. The basic tools of the educational and cognitive process include gaming and entertaining interactive instruments. The park was built according to the world "Science centers" model, drawing from their tested concepts which offer spontaneous education and knowledge acquired through interactive tools (learn by playing).

wrongItems.description: iQPARK is an interactive entertaining and educational science centre situated in Liberec, Czech Republic intended mainly for younger children from 2 to 10 and their parents. It is the first venue of its kind in the Czech Republic. The basic tools of the educational and cognitive process include gaming and entertaining interactive instruments.
